# flatpak-repos.list — Flatpak repository domains for CIDR resolution
#
# Format: one domain per line, comments with #
# Used by: egress/allowlists/update-cidrs.sh (Phase 2 tooling)
# Purpose: resolve to CIDRs → populate flatpak_cidrs set in hisnos-updates.nft
#
# Scope: app installation and updates via Flatpak CLI or GNOME Software.
# Per-application outbound (e.g. Firefox browsing) is handled by OpenSnitch.
#
# Refresh cadence: monthly
# Refresh command: sudo egress/allowlists/update-cidrs.sh --target flatpak

# Flathub — primary Flatpak repository
dl.flathub.org
api.flathub.org
flathub.org

# Flathub content on GitHub
flathub.github.io
raw.githubusercontent.com
objects.githubusercontent.com
github.com

# GNOME Flatpak repository (KDE Discover / GNOME Software default)
sdk.gnome.org
runtime.fedoraproject.org

# KDE Flatpak repository (Plasma 6 apps)
distribute.kde.org

# Freedesktop Platform (runtime dependency for many Flatpak apps)
# Hosted on Fastly CDN — covered by 151.101.0.0/16 static CIDR
dl.flathub.org
